title: Hour 2 - Albert Breer
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Albert Breer
description:
Dan discusses the latest from MLB, including the high-flying Mets. Albert Breer joins the show to discuss the Pro Football Hall of Fame Class of 2022 - including drama over some entries like Tony Boselli.
